00:22:44.850 --> 00:22:47.530
Apakah itu maksudmu, Ghin?

00:22:48.010 --> 00:22:51.470
Iya, tapi...

00:22:51.930 --> 00:22:55.640
Tak kusangka
kapal utama dalam kondisi separah ini.

00:22:55.640 --> 00:22:57.140
Don Krieg!

